#
# Mutations (Assumes Humanoid)
# Roll d10 and see if the result is equal or less than Willpower Bonus.  If it is, let them pick a Primary Mutation Group, instead of Rolling Randomly.


:Start
1,<b><u>Mutations</u></b>{CR~}{Loop~{Dice~1d5},[Basic Primary Mutation Groups]{CR~}}{Loop~{Dice~1d5},[Defects]{CR~}}

:Basic Primary Mutation Groups
