:Uncontrolled Chemical Production
1,Poison Gas – Toxic damage to all within 3 yards
2,Ammonia Gas – All those within 3 yards test Toughness or be affected by a strong ammonia odor that causes all checks to be at -10 percent. 
3,Pheromone Madness – All those within 3 yards test WP or enter blind rage(berserker).  
4,Pheromone Kindness – All those within 3 yards test WP or shift 2 steps towards friendly. 

